title: The Bite Fight (Tyson-Holyfield) EPUB
description:
The Bite Fight: Tyson, Holyfield and the Night That Changed Boxing Forever
By George Willis
2013
EPUB


The infamous boxing match between Mike Tyson and Evander Holyfield on June 28, 1997, was like none other in the sports history, and this insightful account of the anticipation, the gruesome fight itself, and the ongoing aftermath of that one night reveals just how much of an impact it really made.
